Meet Jitar.

0:00:02.600,0:00:08.000
An open-source, distributed runtime
for JavaScript and TypeScript applications.

0:00:08.200,0:00:13.000
On the surface, it looks simple.
But inside, it’s doing something powerful.

0:00:13.100,0:00:16.400
It manages a full-stack
monolithic application.

0:00:16.400,0:00:18.700
Which is loved for its simplicity.

0:00:19.000,0:00:23.300
And with good modularity,
it can even scale for big apps and teams.

