it could take down the whole application.

0:00:42.160,0:00:44.300
And this is where Jitar comes in.

0:00:44.700,0:00:48.100
It provides the tools to overcome these limitations...

0:00:48.100,0:00:51.600
by taking your full-stack 
monolithic application.

