and deploying them across
web browsers and servers.

0:01:00.400,0:01:05.900
Jitar handles the communication automatically,
so everything works seamlessly.

0:01:05.900,0:01:10.300
This gives your application the power
and flexibility of distributed systems...

0:01:10.300,0:01:11.900
exactly when you need it.

0:01:12.320,0:01:16.900
It seamlessly integrates frontend 
and backend, with safe type sharing.

0:01:17.120,0:01:20.300
And it doesn’t lock you into 
any framework or library.

0:01:20.560,0:01:22.200
But it has more to offer.

0:01:22.600,0:01:24.800
It comes with batteries included.

0:01:24.960,0:01:30.400
Like, request routing, load balancing, 
health monitoring, access control, and more.

